            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " has been on my radar since 2023, but the latest round of updates pushed it from \"solid option\" to \"why aren't you using this yet?\"",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "If you're juggling spreadsheets, sticky notes, three different apps, and a prayer every time a client asks for an update — keep reading. This one's for you.",
