          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Contractor Foreman has never been a tool that rests on its laurels. The team ships improvements regularly, and the 2025 cycle is the most impressive yet. Here's what caught my attention:",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Streamlined Estimate Generation",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Creating estimates used to take me forever — digging through old quotes, manually adjusting line items, formatting everything to look professional. Contractor Foreman now offers a faster estimate builder with templates you can customize per project type. You build it once, reuse it dozens of times. My buddy who runs a residential remodeling crew told me he cut his estimate time from 45 minutes to under 12.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Enhanced GPS Time Card Tracking",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Time cards with GPS tracking aren't brand new, but the recent improvements make them significantly more reliable. Workers clock in from the field, you see exactly where they are, and the data flows directly into payroll calculations. No more chasing down timesheets on Friday afternoon. No more guessing who showed up when.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Smoother Online Payment Collection",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Getting paid has always been the least fun part of contracting. The updated payment integration lets clients pay invoices directly through a branded link. It connects to popular processors, and the money lands in your account without you having to follow up three times. Contractors using this feature report faster payment cycles — some getting paid within 24 hours of sending an invoice.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Improved Mobile Experience",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The mobile app got a significant polish. Navigation is snappier, document uploads are more reliable offline, and the dashboard loads faster even on spotty job site connections. If you've ever tried to pull up a change order while standing in mud next to an excavator, you know how much this matters.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Consolidated Dashboard Views",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "One of my favorite additions: the ability to see project health, financial summaries, and team activity in a single consolidated view. Instead of clicking through five screens, you get the full picture at a glance. For busy GCs managing multiple crews across different sites, this alone is worth the switch.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
